# RapidAid Patient Dashboard UI Design

## Purpose

The Patient Dashboard is the central interface for users after logging in. It provides quick access to emergency services, medical information, live tracking, AI assistance, and emergency history.

## Dashboard Layout

### Top Navigation Bar

- 🚑 RapidAid Logo
- Dashboard
- Notifications
- Profile
- Settings
- Logout

## Welcome Section

### Greeting

Welcome back!

Stay prepared. Help is always one tap away.

Display:

- User Name
- Blood Group
- Current Location
- Current Date & Time

---

# Quick Action Cards

## 🚨 Emergency SOS

Large red emergency button.

Functions:

- One-tap SOS
- Capture Live GPS
- Notify Emergency Contacts
- Dispatch Ambulance

---

## 📍 Live Tracking

Features

- Current Location
- Ambulance Live Tracking
- Estimated Arrival Time (ETA)
- Route Information

---

## 🆔 QR Medical Profile

Display

- QR Code
- Blood Group
- Allergies
- Medical Conditions
- Emergency Contacts

Actions

- View QR
- Download QR
- Share QR

---

## 🤖 AI Health Assistant

Features

- Ask Health Questions
- Emergency Guidance
- First Aid Suggestions
- Nearby Hospital Recommendation

---

## 💊 Nearby Pharmacy

Display

- Nearby Pharmacies
- Distance
- Opening Status
- Navigation Button

---

## ⚠ Public Hazard Reporting

Users can report:

- Road Accidents
- Water Logging
- Fire Incidents
- Fallen Trees
- Broken Roads
- Electrical Hazards

Status

- Submitted
- In Progress
- Resolved

---

## 📊 Emergency History

Display

- Date
- Emergency Type
- Hospital Assigned
- Ambulance
- Response Time
- Status

---

## Notifications Panel

Examples

- Ambulance Dispatched
- Hospital Assigned
- Emergency Contact Notified
- QR Profile Updated

---

## Profile Summary

Display

- Name
- Blood Group
- Age
- Emergency Contact
- Medical Conditions

Buttons

- Edit Profile
- Update Medical Information

